com.nokia.payment

Class ProductData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nokia.payment.ProductData

  • public class ProductData
extends java.lang.Object
    Product data class. This class is used to hold together the product code and corresponding price information. To determine, whether it is a valid product (has price associated with it), call isValid() method.
